    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Using Guava you can easily combine different type of criteria. For your specific solution you can use:</p>\n\n<pre><code>value = CharMatcher.inRange('0', '9')\n        .or(CharMatcher.inRange('a', 'z')\n        .or(CharMatcher.inRange('A', 'Z'))).retainFrom(value)\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
