    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Guava's <a href=\"https://guava.dev/releases/19.0/api/docs/com/google/common/base/CharMatcher.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">CharMatcher</a> provides a concise solution:</p>\n\n<pre><code>output = CharMatcher.javaLetterOrDigit().retainFrom(input);\n</code></pre>\n"
