    "body" : "<h1>Dart</h1>\n<p>If you tried this and it didn't work..</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>value.replaceAll(&quot;[^A-Za-z0-9]&quot;, &quot;&quot;);</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Just use RegExp like this:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>value.replaceAll(RegExp(&quot;[^A-Za-z0-9]&quot;), &quot;&quot;);</p>\n</blockquote>\n"
